ygData.messageBody:
Hello,<br>In your younger years, did you do any
quests? I am a lvl 8 human druid, and I got her pretty
decked out in leather with a velium warhammer and a
qeynos kite shield and most of my spells bought for when
I hit lvl 9. I love doing quests, besides hacking
and slashing everything I see--minus bears and wolves
of course!! Go to all everquest sites you can find
with your search engine and look up quests, for either
the zone, race, etc. That is how I have done things
to make plat. I know it may sound trivial especially
to a lvl 26 pally now, but hey each their own ;-)
